title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Aerosoft DHC-6 Twin Otter
description:
In this video we will have a first look at the Aerosoft DHC-6 Twin Otter which has been released earlier today. After reviewing the different models of DHC-6 included in the package we will a short look at where to find the documentation while we are waiting for MSFS 2020 to complete loading. Once loading has completed we will look first from the external part of the aircraft after which we go inside and review the various options available there.
